## Interaction Contract

- The root is a native `<button type="button">`, so it does not submit parent forms by default.
- `disabled` and `loading` both set the native `disabled` attribute and block `click` emission.
- `loading` renders a spinner while preserving button content.
- `primary` only changes the visual style. Non-primary buttons keep the `fake-background` hover layer.
- `mini` switches to the compact size without changing button semantics.
